# Weekly Complement Summary for Suppliers

Each complement can now be configured with email addresses to receive a **weekly summary** of complement counts for the upcoming week. Every Sunday morning, these addresses get an email listing the number of complements needed for each delivery of the week ahead.

This is useful for external suppliers (a baker, a cheese maker, an egg producer) who need to know how much to prepare.

To set it up, open any complement and fill in the new **Notifications** section with the supplier's email addresses.

Depot notification settings have also been moved into their own **Notifications** section for consistency.

Find more information about delivery notifications in [the deliveries handbook](/handbook/deliveries#delivery-notifications).
